{"Id":486,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-mazhonggang","Author":"Ma Zhong Gang","Language":"Chinese(simplified)","Description":"Chinese(simplified)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"https://alquran.cloud/api","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":102,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"[今世]竞相追逐名利已使你们疏忽[履行宗教功修]，"},{"SurahNumber":102,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"直到你们去见坟墓。"},{"SurahNumber":102,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"不，你们不久将知道；"},{"SurahNumber":102,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"不，你们不久将知道；"},{"SurahNumber":102,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"不，假如你们知道真实的知识[竞相追逐名利的后果，你们必定停止了]。"},{"SurahNumber":102,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"你们必将看见火狱。"},{"SurahNumber":102,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"然后，你们必将亲眼看见它；"},{"SurahNumber":102,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"然后，在那日，你们必将被审问[你们在尘世所享受的]恩惠。"}]}